-- China Aims to Develop Rare Earth Mines Overseas, Wall Street Journal Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-12-28T01:12:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-28/china-aims-to-develop-rare-earth-mines-overseas-wall-street-journal-says.html
China seeks to develop rare earth
mines abroad with other countries in response to dwindling
domestic resources, the China Securities Journal reported today,
citing Xu Xu, chairman of the China Chamber of Commerce of
Metals, Minerals and Chemicals Importers and Exporters.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
